// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1013 — Mass File Rename (thegentlemen)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: c23c9609-e1b0-5869-95fa-526c714ced13

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
